column5: Cabin 1 sleeps up to four people with a king size bed and two twin beds in the upstairs loft. The kitchen is supplied with all your cooking and eating utensils, plus a convenient cook top. Regular and Decaf coffee are furnished and kept in the freezer. It has a private bathroom with whirlpool tub.
